From priviledged exec mode:
TO CLEAR CONFIGURATION:
delete vlan.dat
erase startup-config
reload

From config
TO SET A DEFAUL GATEWAY:
ip default-gateway 192.168.100.1

From config-line
SET NO TIMEOUT WHEN CONFIGURING THE ROUTER:
exec-timeout 0 0

PREVENT ROUTER FROM INTERRUPTING YOU WHEN CONFIGURING AN INTERFACE:
logging synchronous

from config
PREVENT ROUTER FROM LOOKING UP A MISTYPED COMMAND:
no ip domain-lookup
